[b]Flashlight Battery[/b]

Adds a rechargeable battery to the default Garry's Mod flashlight. Good for horror, hide and seek, survival, and just realism. 

[b]Features[/b]
[list]
[*]Flashlight drains while in use
[*]Recharges while turned off
[*]Clean battery HUD with position, scale, opacity, and visibility options
[*]Admin settings for drain time, recharge speed, cooldown, and minimum battery required
[*]Optional chat notifications
[*]Works in multiplayer
[/list]

[b]Settings[/b]
[list]
[*]Client settings: HUD corner, visibility, opacity, and scale
[*]Admin settings: enable/disable, drain time, recharge amount, recharge interval, cooldown, minimum battery, and notifications
[/list]

